\fBSee also\fR
.sp 2
   LSB_TIME_MBD, LSB_TIME_SBD, LSF_TIME_LIM, LSF_TIME_RES
.sp 2
\fBLSB_TIME_MBD\fR
.sp 2

.sp 2 .SH "Syntax"
\fBSyntax\fR
.sp 2
   \fRLSB_TIME_MBD=\fR\fItiming_level\fR
.sp 2 .SH "Description"
\fBDescription\fR
.sp 2
   The timing level for checking how long mbatchd routines run.
.sp 2
   Time usage is logged in milliseconds; specify a positive
   integer.
.sp 2
   Example: LSB_TIME_MBD=1
.sp 2 .SH "Default"
\fBDefault\fR
