.sp 2
   The timing level for checking how long sbatchd routines run.
.sp 2
   Time usage is logged in milliseconds; specify a positive
   integer.
.sp 2
   Example: LSB_TIME_SBD=1
.sp 2 .SH "Default"
\fBDefault\fR
.sp 2
   Not defined
.sp 2 .SH "See also"
\fBSee also\fR
.sp 2
   LSB_TIME_CMD, LSB_TIME_MBD, LSF_TIME_LIM, LSF_TIME_RES
